# Message prefix block for com.ibm.ws.kernel.reporting: CWWKF1700 - CWWKF1799

CWWKF1700.reporting.is.enabled=CWWKF1700I: CVE Reporting feature is enabled
CWWKF1700.reporting.is.enabled.explanation=CVE Reporting feature is currently enabled
CWWKF1700.reporting.is.enabled.useraction=To disabled CVE Reporting, specify <cveReporting enabled="false" /> in the server.xml file 

CWWKF1701.reporting.is.disabled=CWWKF1701I: CVE Reporting feature is disabled
CWWKF1701.reporting.is.disabled.explanation=CVE Reporting feature needs to be enabled to run
CWWKF1701.reporting.is.disabled.useraction=To enable CVE Reporting, specify <cveReporting enabled="true" /> in the server.xml file 

open.liberty.resposne=For more information you can review Open Liberty CVEs at https://openliberty.io/docs/latest/security-vulnerabilities.html

websphere.liberty.response=For more information you can review IBM WebSphere Liberty CVEs at https://www.ibm.com/support/pages/node/710969

CWWKF1702.cve.found=CWWKF1702W: Based on a assessment of the Liberty runtime. It is recommended that following CVEs are reviewed: {0}
CWWKF1702.cve.found.explanation=There is something that has been found
CWWKF1702.cve.found.useraction=Follow the message to resolve what has been found

CWWKF1703.cve.not.found=CWWKF1703I: Based on assessment of the Liberty runtime, no applicable CVEs were found.
CWWKF1703.cve.not.found.explanation=There is no problems
CWWKF1703.cve.not.found.useraction=The following message has no issues

CWWKF1704.incorrect.url=CWWKF1704W: The URL specified is not correct and a connection could not be made: {0}
CWWKF1704.incorrect.url.explanation=Due to the URL provided no connection could be made
CWWKF1704.incorrect.url.useraction=Verify that the URL is correct

CWWKF1705.failed.response=CWWKF1705W: Unable to retrieve relevant CVE information due to a communication issue with the CVE Reporting Service.
CWWKF1705.failed.response.explanation=The service was not able to give a response.
CWWKF1705.failed.response.useraction=the service was not able to provide a response.

CWWKF1706.issue.parsing=CWWKF1706W: Issue when parsing Product Information.
CWWKF1706.issue.parsing.explanation=There was an issue when parsing the Product Information.
CWWKF1706.issue.parsing.useraction=the service was not able to successfully parse the product information